              <span class="text-sm font-bold">2</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Add to Home Screen</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                <strong>iOS:</strong> Tap the share button and select "Add to Home Screen"<br>
                <strong>Android:</strong> Tap the menu and select "Add to Home screen"
